name: Goldfish Rescue
desc: You can target 1 monster in your opponent's GY; excavate the top card of your Deck, and if it is a monster with the same Attribute as that target, add it to your hand, and if you do, shuffle that target into the Deck. Otherwise, send the excavated card to the GY, and if you do, destroy this card. You can only use this effect of "Goldfish Rescue" once per turn.
